After the primer extension reaction, the reaction products were transferred to a Greiner Bio-One 96-well microplate for FP measurement on a Paradigm Multi-Mode Microplate Detection Platform under excitation at 535 nm and emission at 585 nm (Beckman Coulter, Brea, CA). Fluorescence polarization value was calculated using the formula:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
